FreshRetailNet-50K XGBoost Temporal FFS
Copyright 2026 Milad Saeedi

This project uses the public FreshRetailNet-50K dataset and compares against values
reported by the FreshRetailNet-50K paper and official baseline repository.

Portions of the experimental notebooks are adapted from or informed by the official
Dingdong-Inc/frn-50k-baseline project, licensed under Apache License 2.0. Modifications
include GPU XGBoost forecasting, temporal cross-validation, Optuna tuning, and
forward-feature-selection experiments.
